# IF GIT SHOWED THAT THIS FILE CHANGED
#
# 1. RUN THE FOLLOWING COMMAND
#
# ---
# git rm --cached '**/*.inlang/.gitignore'
# ---
#
# 2. COMMIT THE CHANGE
#
# ---
# git commit -m "fix: remove tracked .gitignore from inlang project"
# ---
#
# Inlang handles the gitignore itself starting with version ^2.5.
#
# Everything is ignored except settings.json, this .gitignore, and
# cache/plugins/.gitkeep. The .gitkeep keeps the plugin-cache directory
# present on fresh clones (the dir is bind-mounted into the dev container
# and paraglide/inlang writes its plugin cache there); real cache contents
# stay ignored.
*
!settings.json
!.gitignore
!cache/
cache/*
!cache/plugins/
cache/plugins/*
!cache/plugins/.gitkeep
